OL,4,C Denunciations of enemies of the state 
OL,5,C and traitors                          
OL,7,  Traitor Ronnie Bad's attempt to kill  
OL,8,  one of our agents was kountered with  
OL,9,  decisive lethal force.                
OL,11,F Kommandant Stevens was patrolling in  
OL,12,F an armoured troop karrier when Mr Bad 
OL,13,F tried to use his Kia Pikanto as a     
OL,14,F weapon in a deliberate kollision.     
OL,16,F Stevens, fearing for his life bravely 
OL,17,F fought back with a high-explosive     
OL,18,F fragmentation round and neutralised   
OL,19,F the threat.                           
OL,21,F The Bad family has been relocated to  
OL,22,F a reeducation centre for their safety.
